        <p class="hidden-ch">The flexible, supportive New Zealand education system gives students the skills and experience they need to succeed anywhere in the world.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">新西兰的教育体制，灵活而又对学生充满关怀和支持，帮助学生获得伴其终身的技能和受用终身的经历，并能在世界范围内收获成功。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">Students gain the ability to work well with people from different cultures and backgrounds, and learn English by living it - not just by learning it from a textbook.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">在新西兰，孩子可以培养跨文化的合作技能，且让英语文化扎根其内，而非仅仅学习书本知识。</p>
