        <p class="hidden-ch">Safe, politically stable and culturally diverse, New Zealand is ranked one of the most peaceful and least corrupt countries in the world.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">新西兰因其社会安全性、政治稳定性以及文化多样性，被评为世界最和平、最不腐败的国家之一。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">We have a high standard of living, clean air, a healthy lifestyle and quality food and accommodation. </p>
        <p class="hidden-en">新西兰拥有高质量的生活质量标准、清新干净的空气、健康的生活方式以及高质量的食物供给、居住环境。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">Homestays welcome students into a Kiwi family, while institutions provide pastoral care to help students feel happy and well-supported. </p>
        <p class="hidden-en">新西兰的寄宿家庭热情地欢迎国际生融入Kiwi家庭，同时政府以及相关机构还会为国际生提供支持和帮助，以保证国际上能在新西兰快乐地学习和生活。</p>
    </div>
</div>
