        <p class="hidden-ch">Studying in New Zealand is an opportunity for personal growth and development.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">在新西兰锻炼自我、发展自我</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">Gaining skills such as punctuality, time management and confidence help students to become successful and independent adults.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">在这里，孩子将成长为一个守时、善于时间管理、充满自信的人才。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">Your son or daughter can experience another culture, have new adventures and make lifelong friendships in one of the world’s cleanest, most beautiful natural environments.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">在这里，您的孩子将感受另一种文化、开展一段人生旅程、收获陪伴终身的友谊。</p>
    </div>
</div>

