        <p class="hidden-ch">The New Zealand education system’s practical, hands-on learning style gives students a head start in the workforce.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">新西兰的教育体制保证学生的实践能力的成长，为孩子的职业之路奠定坚实的基础。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">Graduates gain internationally-recognised qualifications and valuable personal skills such as the ability to think critically, communicate well and lead a team; a well-rounded combination valued by global employers.  </p>
        <p class="hidden-en">完成高等教育的学子将获得被国际认可的教育资历以及宝贵的个人技能，如辩证的思考能力、出色的沟通能力以及组织领导能力。而这些技能正是获得职业成功的道路。</p>
        <p class="hidden-ch">New Zealand universities and other institutions have a high graduate employment rate, and students may be able to work here after graduation.</p>
        <p class="hidden-en">在新西兰，大学生拥有极高的就业率。您和您的孩子还可以考虑就业新西兰。</p>
    </div>
</div>

